#

Сырники с ягодным соусом и медом

$12.5
320 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

DairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh-Protein

Tags:

BreakfastDessertComfort Food

Description

Delicate cheese pancakes served with a vibrant berry sauce and a drizzle of honey for a sweet finish.

Ingredients

  • Cottage cheese: 500g
  • Eggs: 2
  • Flour: 100g
  • Sugar: 2 tbsp
  • Baking powder: 1 tsp
  • Salt: a pinch
  • Butter: for frying
  • Mixed berries: 200g
  • Honey: to taste
